    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071955_6_5839-5896",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "5839-5896",
      "markText": "如果不能自己安排生活的优先次序， 就只能任由别人替你安排。",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071955&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5839&rangeEnd=5896",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0af32e20813ab829bg015a9c?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5839&rangeEnd=5896"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071955_6_3835-3915",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3835-3915",
      "markText": "精要主义不是如何完成更多的事情，而是如何做好对的事情。它也不是提倡为了少做而少做，而是主张只做必做之事，尽可能做出最明智的时间和精力投资，从而达到个人贡献峰值。",
      "totalCount": 165,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071955&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3835&rangeEnd=3915",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0af32e20813ab829bg015a9c?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3835&rangeEnd=3915"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071955_6_8380-8431",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "8380-8431",
      "markText": "心理学家们称之为“决定疲劳”：要做的决定越多，决定的质量就越差。",
      "totalCount": 136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071955&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8380&rangeEnd=8431",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0af32e20813ab829bg015a9c?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8380&rangeEnd=8431"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071955_5_1996-2033",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1996-2033",
      "markText": "现在，被我们高估的资产就是那种什么都要做、什么都要有和什么都要实现的妄想。",
